lead_paragraph: The confusing case of Vladimir Morozov and Nikita Lobintsev took a new twist on Tuesday when swimming's ruling body said, despite earlier reports, that the Russian duo had not been cleared to compete at the Olympics and still await a final decision.

headline.print_headline: Russian Swimmers Morozov, Lobintsev 'Not Cleared for Rio'
headline.main: Russian Swimmers Morozov, Lobintsev 'Not Cleared for Rio'
